snippet.title: Godzilla Pinball - Gameplay
snippet.description: Save New York! A low run game by Sega (Stern) from 1998, with the overall goal to complete or play together 5 multiballs and then save New York! Not too much to it but a fun quick game to play. This game has some very cool ramp shots and the large Godzilla head on the playfield really stands out. Rewards accurate ramp and lane shots!
